    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0

    v0 = wp.abs((wp.exp(tmp + 0.25) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.15)))
    v0 = (0.75 / (v1 - tmp))
    tmp = v2
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.sin(v1 + 0.24) * 0.37))
    v2 = 0.63
    tmp = v2
    tmp = (0.23 * ((tmp + 0.26 - v1 + 0.20) + (v0 + 0.43 - v0 + 0.84)))
